{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Forget about sitting down or lying down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naturally, without any food and without any sanitary conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For three days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were choking, people were-- just, it was impossible to imagine a-- a-- a transport like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, when you came to Auschwitz, and the doors opened up, we came off this-- this cattle car, and we tried to stay-- the family tried to stay together.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] telling us for the men to go separately and the women to go separately.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were right away separated from each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the men-- again, as far as I know, the men were separated from those who were still looking well enough physically to be-- according to the estimation of the German officer who selected us-- that he is capable for work was placed in one area.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those who were not were placed to a different area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- they were marched away from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the last time I saw them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- and then I was separated-- I-- my brother and I were separated from my father just from this group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever happened to them, from him-- I mean, to him, I never found out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the last time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then my brother and me, we were marched into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before we-- before we came into that barrack, we went to-- we were marched off to a place in front of a-- some sort of barrack, a huge one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were stripped from our clothing, shaved all over, and go in to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
